thread.title: Won Koun Lee
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Won Koun Lee

author: Won Koun Lee
title: Won Koun Lee
text:
Car was clean, well equipped and had no problems.
It was cheap and I saw people waiting in the long queue at other desks in coolangatta airport but I could get my key literally in 5 minutes.
Satisfying service and well explained how to get to the car.
